** story **
once a upon time, in a forest there lived a monkey who resited on a jamoon tree.whitch was on a banked of a river.
in the same forest there lived a crocodile and his wife. one day the crocodile came to the banks of the river and rested under the tree.
the kind hearted monkey offered him some frouts. the crocodile came back the next day for mome frouts, as he loved them. as days passed
by the crocodile and the monkey became good friends. 